{
  "texts": [
    "Our work in [8] was already an introduction to industrial chatbots utilized as I5.0 HMI devices.",
    "In this current research, we empower the industrial chatbot with the latest GPT4-LM, which offers more information and functionalities than its predecessor (GPT3.5), which we used in our earlier chatbot model.",
    "We limited our previous chatbot to an offline version connected to the GPT LM through APIs and only accurately responded to basic queries within the loaded factory data.",
    "In this study, we add an online version that presents more flexibility in terms of information computation, responses, hints, and recommendations beyond the closed-loaded factory data.",
    "The online version is a great factory supervising tool and operator training assistant.Compared to our previous I4.0 auto-parameters configuration system [53], our GPT industrial chatbot integrates two crucial parameters, maximum overtime working hours and maximum factory pollution rate, as additional conditions for production run."
  ]
}